high_descs: Walk up to the small black table against the wall on your right.
Open the drawer of the black table and pick up the watch, then close the drawer.
Walk over to the far side of the glass table behind you.
Put the watch on the white plate that is near the yellow vase on the glass table.
Pick up the white plate with the watch on it off of the glass table.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left to face the small black table to the right of the couch.
Put the plate with the watch on it on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a watch on it on a black table.

high_descs: Step forward and make a right then left at the door. Go to the small desk with a drawer.
Open the drawer and take out a watch,
Turn to the right and carry the watch forward. Make a right and go around to the other side of the large dining table.
Put the watch on the plate.
Pick up the plate with the watch on it.
Turn to the left and go forward, Make a left at the wall.
Place the plate and watch on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the plate with a watch on the table.

high_descs: Walk ahead to the right side of the dining room table to face the small table on the right wall.
Take the watch out of the drawer.
Turn around and walk to the far side of the table.
Place the watch on the white plate.
Pick up the plate.
Turn left and veer left to the small rectangular table with the lamp on it.
Place the plate on the table to the right of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate on a table.
